quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  57,1,"All that is in the heavens and the earth extols the glory of Allah. He is the Most Mighty, the Most Wise.",footnotes:181871:1,footnotes:181872:2
  57,2,"His is the dominion of the heavens and the earth. He gives life and causes death, and He has power over everything."
  57,3,"He is the First and the Last, and the Manifest and the Hidden, and He has knowledge of everything.",footnotes:181873:1